# Lakehouse (Seagate) — Never commit
# The actual FAISS index, ID maps, metadata DB, and corpus live on external storage
# These are environment-specific and too large for version control
/mnt/seagate_ai_corpus/
*.faiss
*.idmap.json
metadata.db

